&lt;p&gt;Deep learning architectures for complex pattern recognition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="learning-outcomes"&gt;Learning Outcomes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By completing this topic, you will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Explain how neurons and layers process information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Describe forward and backward propagation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Choose appropriate activation functions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand when depth helps (and when it doesn&amp;rsquo;t)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
