&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Null hypothesis&lt;/strong&gt;: No difference between variants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;p-value&lt;/strong&gt;: Probability of result under null&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Confidence interval&lt;/strong&gt;: Range of plausible effects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Effect size&lt;/strong&gt;: Magnitude of difference&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id="sample-size-calculation"&gt;Sample Size Calculation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Depends on:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Finance Applications</title><link>https://digital-ai-finance.github.io/ML_Design_Thinking/topics/finance-applications/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://digital-ai-finance.github.io/ML_Design_Thinking/topics/finance-applications/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="finance-applications"&gt;Finance Applications&lt;/h1&gt;
